Summary :-
* recommendation system 
* It's of four type and we use Unsupervised learning for this purpose 
* RBM, Restricted Boltzman Machine
* It's architecture consists of input layer and hidden layer
*There are two process:-
I) forward pass :- in this we data is fed from input layer to hidden layer
II) backward pass :- hidden layer to input layer to reduce the error
* in this architecture the hidden layers  are not connected to input layer each other that's by it is known as Restricted
* Netflix use this recommendation system to provide user recommendation about movies
